<p>86.<b> The following recommendations will be examined by Spain, which will provide 
responses in due course, but no later than the fifteenth session of the Human Rights 
Council, in September 2010.  The response of Spain to these recommendations will be 
included in the outcome report adopted by the Human Rights Council at its fifteenth 
session.  
</b></p>
