<p>86.3.<b> Ratify and implement the International Convention on the Protection 
of the Rights of All Migrant Workers and Members of Their Families (Bolivia);   
</b></p>
<p>86.4.<b> Ratify the International Convention on the Protection of the Rights of 
All Migrant Workers and Members of Their Families as a fundamental step 
towards the protection of human rights (Guatemala);  
</b></p>
<p>86.5.<b> Ratify the International Convention on the Protection of the Rights of 
All Migrant Workers and Members of Their Families, and, by taking that 
