respecting the fundamental freedoms of those affected (Paraguay);   
</b></p>
<p>86.6.<b> Adhere to the International Convention on the Protection of the Rights 
of All Migrant Workers and Members of Their Families (Nicaragua);  
</b></p>
<p>86.7.<b> Pursue its efforts, and continue, to guarantee all human rights; and 
